<div id="reports" class="docs-section">
  <h2>Reports</h2>
  <p>Paperboy includes a reporting tool for generating data exports and summaries of form submissions.</p>

  <h3>Running a Report</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Open <strong>Reports</strong> from the profile dropdown.</li>
    <li>Select the report you want to run.</li>
    <li>Apply any available filters (date range, form type, status, organizational level).</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Generate Report</strong> to run it.</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Scheduled Reports</h3>
  <p>You can schedule reports to run automatically on a recurring basis (daily, weekly, or monthly). Scheduled reports are delivered to your email.</p>
  <ul>
    <li>From the Reports page, click <strong>Scheduled Reports</strong> to view and manage your schedules.</li>
    <li>Use the toggle to enable or disable a scheduled report without deleting it.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
